        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks WDF for his offer of assistance in collecting varieties of poultry. Describes his needs. He will raise his own pigeons.</p>
            <p>Often doubts whether, despite all help, the problem of species will not overpower him.</p>
        </abstract>
